title: Trailer hitch

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for: trailer hitch, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view for a trailer hitch, showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is a left side elevational view thereof, the right side elevational view being a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 3 is a top elevational thereof;
FIG. 4 is a bottom elevational view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a rear elevational view thereof; and,
FIG. 6 is a front elevational view thereof.
The broken lines showing of other parts is for illustrative purposes only and forms no part of the claimed design.
